DMUPreviousCommentCmdHdr.Title: Previous Comment
DMUPreviousCommentCmdHdr.ShortHelp: Navigates to the previous comment in the comments panel.
DMUPreviousCommentCmdHdr.LongHelp: From the first comment, the command navigates to the last comment.
DMUNextCommentCmdHdr.Title: Next Comment
DMUNextCommentCmdHdr.ShortHelp: Navigates to the next comment in the comments panel.
DMUNextCommentCmdHdr.LongHelp: From the last comment, the command navigates to the first comment.
